---
import ScrollReveal from '../ui/ScrollReveal.astro';
---

<section class="relative min-h-[100dvh] flex items-center pt-32 pb-24 md:pt-36 md:pb-28 overflow-hidden" aria-label="Hero">

  <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-5 md:px-8 lg:px-10">
    <div class="max-w-3xl">
      <p class="mb-6 flex items-center gap-3 font-mono text-[11px] tracking-[0.18em] text-text-tertiary uppercase">
        <span class="h-px w-8 bg-primary-500/70" aria-hidden="true" />
        Norware / Sistemas digitales
      </p>
      <h1 class="font-heading text-5xl sm:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-normal leading-[1.03] tracking-[-0.03em] text-text-primary" data-i18n-html="hero.title" style="animation: hero-h1-in 800ms cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) 200ms both;">
        Tu negocio tiene problemas.
        <span class="text-primary-500">Los resolvemos con software</span>
        que funciona.
      </h1>

      <p class="mt-6 text-lg md:text-xl text-text-secondary leading-[1.7] max-w-xl reveal-fade-up" style="transition-delay: 200ms" data-i18n-html="hero.subtitle">
        <span class="text-primary-500">Automatización</span>, <span class="text-primary-500">integración</span>, <span class="text-primary-500">digitalización</span>.
        Identificamos el problema, diseñamos la solución y la implementamos con
        <span class="text-primary-500">equipo senior</span>,
        <span class="text-primary-500">entregas predecibles</span> y cero sorpresas.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-10 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-start gap-4 reveal-fade-up" style="transition-delay: 400ms">
        <a href="#contact" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2.5 px-7 py-3.5 text-[15px] font-semibold tracking-[-0.01em] rounded-md bg-primary-500 text-bg hover:bg-primary-300 active:scale-[0.97] transition-all duration-200 no-underline" data-i18n="hero.cta">
          Empezar un proyecto
          <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M5 3l5 5-5 5" />
          </svg>
        </a>
        <a href="#portfolio" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2.5 px-7 py-3.5 text-[15px] font-semibold tracking-[-0.01em] rounded-lg border border-border text-text-secondary hover:border-primary-500/40 hover:text-primary-500 transition-all duration-200 no-underline" data-i18n="hero.secundario">
          Ver trabajos
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-x-4 gap-y-2 text-sm text-text-tertiary">
        <span class="flex items-center gap-1.5 reveal-fade-up" style="transition-delay: 500ms" data-i18n="hero.stat1">
          <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary-500/60" aria-hidden="true" />
          Proyectos desde $25k
        </span>
        <span class="flex items-center gap-1.5 border-l border-border pl-4 reveal-fade-up" style="transition-delay: 600ms" data-i18n="hero.stat2">
          <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary-500/60" aria-hidden="true" />
          Respondemos en 24 hs
        </span>
        <span class="flex items-center gap-1.5 border-l border-border pl-4 reveal-fade-up" style="transition-delay: 700ms" data-i18n="hero.stat3">
          <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary-500/60" aria-hidden="true" />
          Sin compromiso
        </span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  @keyframes hero-h1-in {
    from { opacity: 0; clip-path: inset(0 0 100% 0); transform: translateY(16px); }
    to   { opacity: 1; clip-path: inset(0); transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    [style*="hero-h1-in"] {
      animation: none !important;
      opacity: 1 !important;
      clip-path: inset(0) !important;
      transform: translateY(0) !important;
    }
  }
</style>
